
Meerkat is a BitTorrent Client written in C++ and C#. Meerkat is freeware and closed source, it was written and released by '47 Software'.

==History==

==Release History==

== Features ==

*Full implementation of the BitTorrent specification
*BitTorrent protocol encryption
*All connections encrypted by default
*Port forwarding via UPnP and NAT PMP
*DHT
*Stop on completion (do not seed mode)

